st know if there are enough of you interested to know how grand this script should be. Post here letting me know 1) What time is best for you (last week in Dec. or first week in Jan). 2) The Class you are going to bring (this will most likely be in Gfay this first time, but evil races are welcome to spice things up). 3) If you have any ideas to add to this event.<br>
